  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0baf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0ba4 \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf - \u0b85\u0ba8\u0bc1\u0bb0\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Government attempts to implement Prohibition of Terrorism Act - Anurakumara Dissanayake",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The government tries to stifle people's protests through repression. People's Liberation Front (JVP) leader Anurakumara Dissanayake said that the government is taking steps to implement the Anti-Terrorism Act amid this situation.",
        "He mentioned this in a special statement issued following the implementation of the state of emergency on Wednesday.",
        "If we do not think and act now, we will have to go towards massive destruction. We are now on the brink of extinction. This is because the Speaker had announced on the 9th that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa will announce his resignation today. However, no action has been taken so far (till noon today).",
        "Instead, it is reported that Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has been appointed as the Acting President. The government including Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe is trying to control the protests of the people by using the powers given to it through repression.",
        "In addition, Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has ordered the implementation of the state of emergency and curfew in the Western Province. In the midst of this, there are also reports that the government is taking steps to implement the Anti-Terrorism Act. This is a wrong practice.",
        "The government should take steps to provide peaceful solutions to the existing problems in the country. Instead of trying to stifle the protests through repression, it will cause massive destruction.",
        "So we urge you to listen to the voice of the people and fulfill their demands. He said that we request the security forces to act on behalf of the people."
      ],
